The same TB is used as common sequence library and for verification of the small AXE AXI IPs.

***COMMON SEQUENCE LIBRARY***
Common sequence library TB has one on one master VIP: slave VIP connections.
Test are run without addition of any specific GLOBAL DEFINES in command line.

***AXE AXI IPs***
To run test cases on following IPs, please include global defines in command line as given below:

1. axe_axi_riscv_amos
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_RISCV_AMOS"

2. axe_axi_riscv_lrsc 
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_RISCV_LRSC"

3. axe_axi_atop_filter
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_ATOP_FILTER"

4. axe_axi_atu
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_ATU"

5. axe_axi_demux
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_DEMUX"

6. axe_axi_dw_converter
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_DW_CONVERTER"

7. axe_axi_err_sub
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_ERR_SUB"

8. axe_axi_id_remap
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_ID_REMAP"

9. axe_axi_isolate
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_ISOLATE"

10. axe_axi_modify_address
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_MODIFY_ADDRESS"

11. axe_axi_mux
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_MUX"

12. axe_axi_riscv_atomics
command example: make run_vsim GLOBAL_DEFINES+="+define+AXE_AXI_RISCV_ATOMICS"

